  "detailed_description": "The year is 2050 and a new pastime has replaced off-season hockey as Canada's official summer sport - the Canadian Robot Racing League.<br><br>Canadian Robot Racing League is a 1-8 person local multiplayer platformer and survival challenge. Inspired by classic platformers of the past and designed as a party game to be picked up and enjoyed by anyone. Controls are simple but the levels will test your platforming skills. Each level has a wide range of deadly hazards you will need to avoid, but don't fall behind or the Gear-Wall will crush you instead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/8904fa17a829e1e471ec976cd96059b2.poster.avif?t=1722961990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/8904fa17a829e1e471ec976cd96059b2.webm?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/8904fa17a829e1e471ec976cd96059b2.mp4?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play with 1-8 players in local multiplayer<br></li><li>Completely free, no microtransactions, loot boxes or ads<br></li><li>Simple controls, for anyone to pick up and play, but extremely challenging levels<br></li><li>Dozens and dozens of deadly hazards - avoid the Spinning Gears, dodge the No-Collision Cannonballs, and hold on when someone flips a Gravity Switch<br></li><li>Over 100 levels to test your platformer skills, taking you from high in the sky, to the Great Canadian Pyramids, underwater, outer space and more</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/3545b37e8cade608fcbeaabd09c84a0f.poster.avif?t=1722961990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/3545b37e8cade608fcbeaabd09c84a0f.webm?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/3545b37e8cade608fcbeaabd09c84a0f.mp4?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Note - Local multiplayer does require at least 1 controller.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/c827cb7ff592ed1130ea2c33d648c0e9.poster.avif?t=1722961990\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/c827cb7ff592ed1130ea2c33d648c0e9.webm?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/c827cb7ff592ed1130ea2c33d648c0e9.mp4?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The year is 2050 and a new pastime has replaced off-season hockey as Canada's official summer sport - the Canadian Robot Racing League.<br><br>Canadian Robot Racing League is a 1-8 person local multiplayer platformer and survival challenge. Inspired by classic platformers of the past and designed as a party game to be picked up and enjoyed by anyone. Controls are simple but the levels will test your platforming skills. Each level has a wide range of deadly hazards you will need to avoid, but don't fall behind or the Gear-Wall will crush you instead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/8904fa17a829e1e471ec976cd96059b2.poster.avif?t=1722961990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/8904fa17a829e1e471ec976cd96059b2.webm?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/8904fa17a829e1e471ec976cd96059b2.mp4?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play with 1-8 players in local multiplayer<br></li><li>Completely free, no microtransactions, loot boxes or ads<br></li><li>Simple controls, for anyone to pick up and play, but extremely challenging levels<br></li><li>Dozens and dozens of deadly hazards - avoid the Spinning Gears, dodge the No-Collision Cannonballs, and hold on when someone flips a Gravity Switch<br></li><li>Over 100 levels to test your platformer skills, taking you from high in the sky, to the Great Canadian Pyramids, underwater, outer space and more</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/3545b37e8cade608fcbeaabd09c84a0f.poster.avif?t=1722961990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/3545b37e8cade608fcbeaabd09c84a0f.webm?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/3545b37e8cade608fcbeaabd09c84a0f.mp4?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Note - Local multiplayer does require at least 1 controller.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/c827cb7ff592ed1130ea2c33d648c0e9.poster.avif?t=1722961990\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/c827cb7ff592ed1130ea2c33d648c0e9.webm?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1199200/extras/c827cb7ff592ed1130ea2c33d648c0e9.mp4?t=1722961990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
